This is Perl module Malts.

INSTALLATION

Install cpanm (App::cpanminus) and then run the following command to install
Malts:

    $ cpanm Malts

If you get an archive of this distribution, unpack it and build it
as per the usual:

    $ tar xzf Malts-$version.tar.gz
    $ cd Malts-$version
    $ perl Makefile.PL
    $ make && make test

Then install it:

    $ make install

DOCUMENTATION

Malts documentation is available as in POD. So you can do:

    $ perldoc Malts

to read the documentation online with your favorite pager.

